@startuml reservation_canselling
title Отмена резервирования товара

actor "Клиентское приложение" as Client
participant "API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "Сервис резервирования" as ReservationService
database "Распределенный кеш" as Cache
database "Хранилище резервов" as ReservationStore
database "Хранилище событий" as EventStore
queue "Event Bus" as EventBus

Client -> Gateway: DELETE /api/v1/reservations/{reservationId}\nREST/HTTPS\nIdempotency-Key
activate Gateway

Gateway -> Gateway: Проверка токена доступа,\nпроверка прав,\nограничение частоты запросов

Gateway -> ReservationService: CancelReservation(reservationId)\nREST или gRPC / HTTP/2\nIdempotency-Key
activate ReservationService

ReservationService -> ReservationStore: Проверка Idempotency-Key
activate ReservationStore

alt Повторный запрос с тем же Idempotency-Key
    ReservationStore --> ReservationService: Ранее сохраненный результат
    deactivate ReservationStore

    ReservationService --> Gateway: 200 OK\nРезультат ранее выполненной отмены
    deactivate ReservationService

    Gateway --> Client: 200 OK\nРезерв уже отменен
    deactivate Gateway

else Новый запрос
    ReservationStore --> ReservationService: Запрос ранее не выполнялся
    deactivate ReservationStore

    ReservationService -> ReservationStore: SELECT reservation\nstatus, skuId, storeId
    activate ReservationStore

    alt Резерв не найден
        ReservationStore --> ReservationService: not found
        deactivate ReservationStore

        ReservationService --> Gateway: 404 Not Found
        deactivate ReservationService

        Gateway --> Client: 404 Not Found
        deactivate Gateway

    else Резерв уже отменен или завершен
        ReservationStore --> ReservationService: status = CANCELLED / EXPIRED
        deactivate ReservationStore

        ReservationService --> Gateway: 200 OK\nРезерв уже неактивен
        deactivate ReservationService

        Gateway --> Client: 200 OK
        deactivate Gateway

    else Активный резерв найден
        ReservationStore --> ReservationService: status = ACTIVE,\nskuId,\nstoreId
        deactivate ReservationStore

        ReservationService -> Cache: Захват распределенной блокировки\nпо skuId + storeId
        activate Cache

        alt Блокировка не получена
            Cache --> ReservationService: lock rejected
            deactivate Cache

            ReservationService --> Gateway: 409 Conflict\nОперация временно недоступна
            deactivate ReservationService

            Gateway --> Client: 409 Conflict\nПовторить позже
            deactivate Gateway

        else Блокировка получена
            Cache --> ReservationService: lock acquired
            deactivate Cache

            ReservationService -> ReservationStore: UPDATE reservation\nstatus = CANCELLED
            activate ReservationStore
            ReservationStore --> ReservationService: OK
            deactivate ReservationStore

            ReservationService -> EventStore: APPEND ReservationCancelled
            activate EventStore
            EventStore --> ReservationService: eventId
            deactivate EventStore

            ReservationService -> EventBus: Publish ReservationCancelled
            activate EventBus
            EventBus --> ReservationService: ack
            deactivate EventBus

            ReservationService -> Cache: DECR reserved_qty\nОсвобождение блокировки
            activate Cache
            Cache --> ReservationService: OK
            deactivate Cache

            ReservationService --> Gateway: 200 OK\nРезерв отменен
            deactivate ReservationService

            Gateway --> Client: 200 OK
            deactivate Gateway
        end
    end
end

@enduml